POLAR CLAW, &quot;and the rest of his team, and you will go find out what
is going on and fix it if you can.&quot;

POLAR CLAW nodded, &quot;The shuttle has been repaired and energized for
the trip.&quot; He said his deep tones.

PROWL, who was standing next to POLAR CLAW glanced up, &quot;Yes, we can
use all the hands we can get. We have no idea what&#39;s going on down
there.&quot;

WOLFGANG and RAMULUS also stood at the ready, WOLFGANG grinning, &quot;Back
into the saddle again he?&quot; He said to NIGHTSHIFT.

&quot;I hope it turns out better than last time.&quot; RAMULUS said only half jokingly.

ELDER smiled, &quot;Good.&quot; He said rubbing his hands together. &quot;Legacy has
fed the coordinates into the shuttle&#39;s navigation systems.&quot;

He turned to look at POLAR CLAW and NIGHTSHIFT, &quot;be as quick as you
can, and we will be awaiting any word.&quot; He shrugged slightly, &quot;Unlike
those in the jungle area the com systems appears to be working. So
keep in contact.&quot;

He glanced at NIGHTSHIFT, &quot;And Bump will be here should we have any
injuries.&quot; He smiled as he said that, trying to lighten the mood with
humor.

